Package: ScSpTITH
Title: ScSpTITH: A Rank-Correlation Framework for Robust Quantification of Multi-Dimensional Tumor Heterogeneity
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jiangti", family = "Luo", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "luojiangti@stu.cpu.edu.cn"),
